Defining Characteristic: Shield-tipped tail, looks like she has a fire inside her at all times
Personality: Usually sweet and kind, but jumpy and unwilling to accept her fate. 
Special Power: Can absorb items into her plasma form to sustain herself, after which they linger on her limbs for a while

Name: Malachite 
Human Name: Kakyoin Noriaki
Age: about 1,700,000
Human Age: 17
Defining Characteristic: flowing hair, has a gem-tipped tail
Personality: ~~ruthless bastard~~ polite, open-minded, blunt at times, he is pretty distant and keeps most relationships at an arms length, only actually getting close to a few people (Polaris), he likes teasing people
Special Power: tentacles 🐙🐙🐙

Name: freila
Human Name:Trish Una
Age: 1,400,000
Human Age:15
Defining Characteristic:Green gem at the end of her tail, Glowing hair 
Personality:Shes somewhat peppy, and has a high taste. She is a very determined individual with the people that she trusts.
Special Power:anything she touches turns soft, making it somewhat indestructible.  Where ever she walks turns soft and squishy due to this.

**Name:** Polaris
**Human Name:** Jotaro Kujo
**Age:** 1,700,000
**Human Age:** 17
**Defining Characteristic:** glowing freckles, glowing eyes, tail flows like a galaxy, ripped end of beanie floats like ashes
**Personality:** pretty shy and reserved, though its mostly out of protection. with those they love, they'll be really touchy feely with (never in public unless the lack of affection is just *that strong*). out of everyone you meet, Polaris is one you can trust to keep a secret until their death.
**Special Power:** being a Savior, Polaris is able to mess with time and space a bit. they can create portals to anywhere/anytime they know of, but they can only do it once every once in a while because of just how much energy it zaps from them

Name:Glorioso
Human Name:luminoso Panettone Fastidiosa
Age: 1,700,000
Human Age:24
Defining Characteristic:The palms of his hands glow, a really thin tail, and only parts of his eyes glow.
Personality:Extremely zealous and active, due to the fact he doesnt have any sense of personal space. He can be somewhat sensible but it doesnt happen that much. He can be somewhat aggressive when people that hes close to or trusts gets threatened. Hes very much chaotic but he can pull his own weight.
Special Power:He can teleport anywhere he wants to in the world. But only in the current time. The further the distance the more energy it takes from him. So he really only uses it to catch up to people or to travel to another state in a short distance.

Name: Caeli
Human Name: Narancia
Age: 1,000,000
Human Age: 17
Defining Characteristic: he has feathers on his arms
Personality: he's a playful prankster. He's a bit rude and not very uptight, but his heart is in the right place. 
Special Power: he can fly

Name: Shale
Human Name: Jolyne
Age: 1, 600, 000
Human Age: 19
Defining Characteristic: There are always strings wrapped around her fingers, she has a butterfly at the end of her tail and on her wrist
Personality: Cheeky and confident, a good leader and older sister.
Special Power: Her tail can split into separate sections and extend to grab things/swing from

Name: Argenti 
Human name: Jean Pierre Polnareff
Age: 2,100,000
Human age: 22
Defining characteristics: Tall hair, metal arms and legs, has a rapier
Personality: Kind hearted, thirsty for justice, hopeless romantic, not the brightest, picky 
Special power: He can move at nearly the speed of light and is excellent with a sword

Name: Akosua 
Human name: Maria Tyler
Age: 1,875,000
Human age: 19
Defining characteristics: Very colorful. 
Personality: Naive, easily excitable, has abandonment issues, doesn't know limits, has no filter, wants the best for everyone 
Special power: She can concentrate light and energy into her very being

Name: Venor
Human Name: Bella Ignes Kishibe
Age: 1 500 000
Human Age: 17
Defining Characteristic: Hair is always floating around, she has many eyes in her hair, she has white crack patterns all over her skin, and her tail loops around 
Personality: Dramatic around her friends, incredibly frightened anywhere else. She never admits shes scared. Or happy. Or anything else, for that matter.
Special Power: Her words can hypnotize people. Literally. She speaks and it looks like she has smoke coming out of her mouth. That hypnotized people. She can turn that off and on

Name: Tourmaline 
Human Name: Bruno Bucciarati 
Age: 1,900,000
Human Age: 20
Defining Characteristic: Eyes that look like the deepest pits of the ocean, as well as markings on their chest that don’t look like they belong on ones skin, almost like closed portals. Their shoulders also seem to be like they are connected by similar forces to that of a zipper. 
Personality: They’re a compassionate figure with the willpower to defend those that they care deeply for. That being said, they are also deeply loyal to those that they have known and care for to the point of fighting anyone who tries to lay a finger on them. Yet, they also have the courage to go up against those who they view as immoral based on their actions prior. Yet they also seem to make weird analogies at times as well as slightly confusing actions.
Special Power: The ability to open up zipper like openings or conjure zippers on objects.

**Name: **Ombrage
**Human Name: **Violette Midnight
**Age:** 1 700 000
**Human Age:** 17
**Defining Characteristic: **Long and Flowy Shadow-like hair, glowing yellow markings (like stars in the night), end of tail like their the hair.
**Personality:** They are very shy and reserved, having a hard time opening up to anyone. They are very emotional and sensible, and tend to get anxious or scared easly. They tend be a coward, and prefer to protect rather than attack. They care deeply about the ones they're close with, and will try their best to help them in hard times.
**Special Power: **They can use their hair to turn into a shadow.

Name: Alamani 
Human Name: Reimi Sugimoto 
Age: 1,700,000
Human Age: 17 
Defining Characteristic: Soft pink hair that seems to be littered with a golden glow being accompanied by what seems like a halo and deep markings on their back that resemble jagged lines that shine with a bright light depending on her emotions. She also seems to have a glowing light that consistently surrounds her neck. While her eyes hold a firm almost knowing glow to them.
Personality: She is generally an amiable woman that is always grateful to be in the company of other people. She also has a deep love for dogs and other creatures going out of their way to pet any dogs they see as long as they accept it. That being said she can also be very firm and harsh towards those that have harmed her or her friends not caring if their strength is greater than hers. She may or may not also have a grudge towards the artist David Bowie. 
Special Power: The ability to bring forth what has happened in ones past if they’ve died in a past life or experienced a near death experience.

Name:Vern
Human Name:Porchetta
Age: 1,400,000
Human Age:16
Defining Characteristic: Constantly floating hair, hair containing what looks like tons of stars and streaks, shimmering blue scales on their shoulders and around their neck, and a tail splitting at the end.
Personality:They usually Lock down most of their emotions, only showing mild emotions. Despite that they really care for everyone around them. They’re very polite to people older than them & are usually formal. They can get mildly enraged if they do catch someone lying. They dont warm up to people until a very long time. They dont show active fear to the ones they’re scared of.
Special Power:If they touch someone, they can tell if they’re lying no matter what. Even if the person thinks its the truth it will still come out as a lie to them. They can create weapons out of the lies if they can collect enough.

Name: Anguis 
Human Name: Cadence Rudd
Age: 1,900,000
Human Age: 17
Defining Characteristic: a looong braid, slit eyes, and **snake tail** (the tail is literally a snake.) (she named it chomps.)
Personality: just like her human counterpart, is known as a delinquent among the muns, sometimes oblivious, but still good intentioned.
Special Power: she can turn any part of her body into an extremely corrosive liquid, the parts can reform.

Name: Solum
Human Name: Tenshi 
Age: 1,800,000
Human Age: 18
Defining Characteristic: cracked, porcelain like skin, a broken halo, pure white eyes. 
Personality: quiet, always has a smile on his face, though never genuine, has very little self respect. Probably internally crying, 
Special Power: can levitate himself,

Name: Quartz 
Human Name: Shizuka Joestar
Age: 1,600, 000
Human Age: 16
Defining Characteristic: Quartz like crystals on the tip of her tail, a star mark on her lower right side. 
Personality: She's a very energic person, and she's also a trickster. She gets bored easly and tend to fight to quit her boredom. She like causing chaos and watching it from afar. She like to spy on people and flirt. 
Special Power: She can turn invisible.

Name: Iuvenis 
Human Name: Hoshi Aohoshi 
Age: 900,000
Human Age: 9
Defining Characteristic: stripped skin, and a glowing star on his tail
Personality: he’s selectively mute, only talking to those he feels safe around, though when he does, he’s extremely bubbly and energetic. When around strangers, he’s creepily silent, and observant
Special Power: he can erase memories and create fabricated ones, though the fake memories can be seen through, and the original memories aren’t entirely destroyed.

Name: Spectra
Human Name: Deaco Nageki
Age: 1753900
Human Age: 17 
Defining Characteristic: Sharp green eyes, she has a set of three horns on the left side of her head/face, constatly wearing a sweater, has a *long* ponytail that often fools people into thinking she has more than one tail. 
Personality: A recluse, but unwaveringly kind and understanding. She seems to not be able to figure people out that well, although she hardly talks to people which may contribute to the problem.
Special Power: Able to warp small amounts of space, accessing the 'code' of the space and being able to rewrite it.

Name: Midnight
Human Name: Chikikuo Yonaka 
Age: 1800069
Human Age: 18
Defining Characteristic: Short (for a mun) and kind of frail looking, often wears extremely long coats. Has noticeable green lines running through her eyes, resembling scars. 
Personality: A rash and kind of  reckless girl, she puts herself into danger without a second thought. However, she's actually quite introverted and nervous around people. 
Special Power: She can ignore the laws of physics entirely if she feels like it. That's it thats the power. Might have a stand I need to work on that.

(I'll be honest, I had to cut some things from his personality to make him work.)
Name: Memphis (I have nothing better.) 
Human Name: Karui Yonaka
Age: 1820000
Human Age: 18
Defining Characteristic: Crystalline appearance, lacks a mouth. 
Personality: Introverted and kind of creepy, he seems to be oddly obsessed with the dark and shadows. 
Special Power: Manipulation of shadows and can change their form at will using this - often masquerades as Midnight, although the lack of a mouth still remains.

Name: Reverie
Human Name: Nobuyuki Darquesse 
Age:  1800002
Human Age: 18
Defining Characteristic: One of his eyes is permanently closed and leaking a lot of colourful goop seemingly constantly. 
Personality: Shy and kind of anxious around new people, Reverie prefers small groups rather than large crowds. He tries his best with things, but is often crushed under regret after doing something. 
Special Power: Necromancy. Might as well keep that consistent.

Name: Lunara
Human Name: Luna Nevermind
Age:  2600009
Human Age: 26
Defining Characteristic: A huge gash in her abdomen that never seems to heal
Personality: Ultra Low temperament towards saviors, acceptance towards scouts and reapers. She has a bad habit of trying to atack anyone who she meets anew due to long gone trust issues that led to her abdomen being torn open once
Special Power: Having an extremely cool scythe, and reaping heart

Name: Anyko [ May change ]
Human Name: Elizabeth Terine
Age: 1856000
Human Age: 18
Defining Characteristic: Her face and arms are dotted with star shaped markings. Tall, at around 13'
Personality: Loud, brash and constantly picking fights. Admittedly, she may be a bit stupid. She tends to react quite vocally to things, and isn't good at hiding how she feels about things.
Special Power: Liz's stand, Backstreet Boys is a set of 5 units. They're quite powerful, although they have a small range. However, they can 'chain' together their ranges to extend the range of one of the units. Each one has a different personality

Name: Rogue [Perditio]
Human Name: Inara 'Lady Luck' 
Age:  1900089
Human Age: 19
Defining Characteristic: Carries a journal with her, No memory
Personality: Lost, Angry and drunk, She's absolutely lost in the void
Special Power: Create, Be unharmed and turn liquids into acid

Name: Resona
Human Name: Hibiki Minami
Age: 1742000
Human Age: 17
Defining Characteristic: Tüba. ... She's rarely seen without it.
Personality: Probably a bit too attached to the Tüba she carries around. She has a constant smile, and is generally quite open to new people.
Special Power: Tüba. ...A Tüba so powerful it physically creates a shockwave if played right.

Name: Ketsuban
Human Name: Ren Lavender Anedepami
Age: 1766848
Human Age: 17
Defining Characteristic: She has skeletal wings protruding from her back, and generally tends to glitch out a lot. This also affects her voice.
Personality: Ketsuban is quite distant to pretty much everyone and constantly gives short answers to things to most people. She also seems really tired. She constantly is in fear of her own glitchy state, hating her usual mun form to the point that she hides as other muns as to not cause it to spread. She constantly feels she has to be extremely careful as to not break something or someone.
Special Power: She's kinda glitchy, which means she can no-clip through stuff sometimes,as well as things that really shouldn't happen happening.. However, the downside of this is that it can also affect other muns or places temporarily.

Name:
Human Name: Arthas Lordaeron
Age: 1842000
Human Age:
Defining Characteristic: Wears armour that seems to unravel  akin to a ribbon sometimes. Has an odd marking on one of his cheeks, and a long tail with a few things sticking off of it resembling leaves. 
Personality: He might glare a lot, but he's actually quite easygoing and calm, having quite a bit of patience for people most of the time. 
Special Power: He has a stand named (I Am) All Of Me. I don't have a clue what it does yet.
